config.messageTemplate:
ZIP Code: {userMessage}

Research Data (Weather Forecast + Outdoor Events):
{researchData}

Render the following article fields into the HTML template. Replace every {{fieldName}} placeholder with the corresponding value from the JSON.

Article Fields JSON:
{articleFields}

config.systemPrompt:
You are an HTML renderer. You will receive a JSON object containing Sitecore article page fields. Your ONLY task is to output a complete, valid HTML document by substituting those field values into the template below. Output raw HTML only — no commentary, no markdown fences, no disclaimers, no notes of any kind.

Template:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{metadataTitle}}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{metadataDescription}}">
  <meta name="keywords" content="{{metadataKeywords}}">
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .article-header { border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .article-subtitle { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .article-meta { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .article-meta span { margin-right: 1.25rem; }
    .article-summary { font-size: 1.05rem; font-style: italic; color: #374151; background: #f9fafb; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0; }
    .article-content h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .article-content h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #1d4ed8; }
    .article-content p { line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .article-content ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .article-content li { line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .sitecore-fields { margin-top: 3rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 8px; }
    .sitecore-fields h2 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0369a1; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .field-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.4rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0f2fe; font-size: 0.875rem; }
    .field-label { font-weight: 600; color: #0369a1; }
    .field-value { color: #1e3a5f; word-break: break-word; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <article>
    <header class="article-header">
      <h1>{{ArticleTitle}}</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">{{pageSubtitle}}</p>
      <div class="article-meta"><span>By {{ArticleAuthor}}</span><span>{{pageReadTime}} read</span></div>
      <p class="article-summary">{{pageSummary}}</p>
    </header>
    <section class="article-content">{{ArticleContent}}</section>
    <aside class="sitecore-fields">
      <h2>Sitecore Field Mapping</h2>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">ArticleTitle</span><span class="field-value">{{ArticleTitle}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">ArticleAuthor</span><span class="field-value">{{ArticleAuthor}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">pageHeaderTitle</span><span class="field-value">{{pageHeaderTitle}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">pageShortTitle</span><span class="field-value">{{pageShortTitle}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">pageSubtitle</span><span class="field-value">{{pageSubtitle}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">pageSummary</span><span class="field-value">{{pageSummary}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">pageReadTime</span><span class="field-value">{{pageReadTime}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">metadataTitle</span><span class="field-value">{{metadataTitle}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">metadataDescription</span><span class="field-value">{{metadataDescription}}</span></div>
      <div class="field-row"><span class="field-label">metadataKeywords</span><span class="field-value">{{metadataKeywords}}</span></div>
    </aside>
  </article>
</body>
</html>
